    ('Guerrilla Tactics', 'At the end of your opponent’s turn, if this unit is more than 6" away from all enemy models, you can remove this unit from the battlefield and place it into Ongoing Reserves.'), 
    ('Fury of the First', 'Each time a model in this unit makes an attack, you can ignore any or all modifiers to that attack’s WS characteristic and/or to the Hit roll. In addition, each time a model in this unit makes an attack that targets the enemy unit you selected for the Oath of the Moment special rule this turn, add 1 to the Hit roll.'),
    ('Vow-sworn Bladesmen', 'At the start of the Fight phase, you can select one of the following effects to apply to melee weapons equipped by models in this unit until the end of the phase:
