    ('Battle Protocols', 'At the start of the battle, if this model is leading a KASTELAN ROBOTS unit, that unit enters Aegis Protocols. In your Command phase, you can select one protocol for that unit to enter. Once a unit enters a protocol, it remains in that protocol until it enters a different one.
