    ('Magic’s Arcane', 'A unit of 11-15 Pink Horrors generates 2 Warp Charge points instead of 1; a unit of 16-20 Pink Horrors instead generates 3 Warp Charge points. A unit of 11-20 Blue Horrors generates 2 Warp Charge points instead of 1.'),
