    ('Master of Blades', 'While this model is leading a unit, each time a model in that unit makes a melee attack, add 1 to the Wound roll. Drazhar can only join friendly units of Incubi. Whilst Drazhar is part of an Incubi unit, all Incubus and Klaivex models in the unit gain 1 Attack.'),
